Subject: [PATCH 5/5] Document OpenAI Codex OAuth and zero-config in-app model
 switching

Documents grok openai login/status/logout, device-code login, credential
storage, the credential-gated built-in openai-codex catalog, and pi-style
/model provider/model:effort syntax. Clarifies that OpenAI API-key
Responses models remain supported separately and no config.toml edit is
needed for ChatGPT Plus/Pro OAuth.
